sp.p:
uneasily Ahem! gaily Oh, well; old friends–so much the better;
      make the visit the more agreeable for my part. I was once fortunate enough to be acquainted
      with Miss Brandon, but it was a mere flying acquaintance.

Then I shall go and join a tribe of Chocktaw Indians, get tattooed, and live comfortably;
      but don't let's talk any more about it we've got the week before us, and we'll amuse
      ourselves. aside I shall begin by making you two comfortable.
